@echasnovski Today It's happening again.. Now I am using gitsign. so I think it's not mini.diff issue anymore..

Here is a video: 

https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8225cc24-5110-430f-9fe0-313312f2fb11

Just in case this helps @luukvbaal

## üõ†Ô∏è Crash Summary
App: NVIM v0.12.0-dev-608+gb92e3889fe
Build type: RelWithDebInfo
LuaJIT 2.1.1744317938

macOS Version: 15.5 (24F74)

